    The day after the incident with the Dinobots, and the stolen pod, Aracnia 
takes a few minutes to reflect on her goals. She became the Commander so 
Megatron could take control. She would have to contact him and make the 
arrangements for him to Command. And now the Terricons were agianst her! That 
was laughable. Once Megatron got here, they would be sorry.
    Entering the bridge she saw Paralysis alert, loading and fidgeting with 
his pistol. "Report." She said bluntly, taking the command chair.
    "So far, so good. Nothing really to report." He craoked, looking into the 
plasma chamber of his gun with one large green eye.
    Aracnia shighed. If she was going to contact Megatron, she had better do 
it now. Taking the comm unit, she contacted Megatron.
    "Megatron, this is Black Aracnia. Please respond. We need to talk, its 
important."
